# ib_sentry_wrapper_backend


## setup virtualenv

```sh
pip install virtualenv
virtualenv .venv
```

## install requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

# if you ran into any issue with kerbrose package install below system dependencies
sudo apt-get install krb5-config libkrb5-dev libssl-dev libsasl2-dev libsasl2-modules-gssapi-mit

```

## running django management commands & usage

```sh
source .venv/bin/activate
export DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=ib_sentry_wrapper_backend.settings.local
python manage.py build -a ib_sentry_wrapper
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser
python manage.py runserver
```

ib_sentry_wrapper
=================

3.0.1 (2024-10-27)
++++++++++++++++++
 - Breaking change
 - Add support for django==4.2
 - Drop support for django<4.2

2.1.2 - (2024-10-27)
--------------------
 - updated sentry-sdk package version -> 1.14.0

2.1.1 - (2024-09-17)
--------------------
 - Code Cleanups


2.1.0 - Apr 30th 2024
---------------------
- Skip logging 401 and 403 exceptions in sentry

2.0.0 - Aug 5th 2022
---------------------
- Update packages in requirements.txt to latest versions
- Remove unused packages from requirements.txt
- Add dependencies_update.md file to give info about requirement updates


1.0.7 - April 3rd 2022
-------------------
- Added app version tag if present in header


1.0.6 - Feb 26, 2021
-------------------
- skipping /adds.txt as well
- added 3 additional tags in sentry logs [client_ip_address, user_agent, browser_session_id]
- handled 403 response


1.0.5 - Nov 10, 2020
-------------------
- skipping /robots.txt as well


1.0.4 - May 12, 2019
-------------------
- Reverted changes in 1.0.3 and only skipping /favicon.ico


1.0.3 - May 12, 2019
-------------------
- Modified 404 http response to logging from sentry errors


1.0.2 - Apr 29, 2019
-------------------
- Modified 401 response sentry logging and enabled sentry errors for 404 status code


1.0.1 - Jun 26, 2019
-------------------
- Added support for attach_stacktrace=True


1.0.0 - Jun 26, 2019
-------------------
- Python 3 support


0.0.5 - May 162019
-------------------
- Changes in 4xx middleware


0.0.4 - Apr 28 2019
-------------------
- Added dsu data middleware


0.0.3 - Apr 25 2019
-------------------
- Added response status code 4xx 5xx middleware


0.0.2 - Apr 25 2019
-------------------
- Added zappa sentry handler and custom middleware


0.0.1 - Apr 25 2019
-------------------
- Initial version
